til-found\"` on collapsed panels (browser find-in-page support)"},"436":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-36","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#aria","content":"Panels with `minSize` override `aria-hidden` to keep collapsed content accessible"},"437":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-37","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Use `minSize` + `maxSize` for sidebar patterns where collapsed content stays visible."},"438":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-38","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"`FocusScope` is opt-in. Don't combine `contain={true}` with `shouldDismissOnBlur` (trapped focus can't leave to trigger blur)."},"439":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-39","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Collapsed panels use `hidden=\"until-found\"` for browser find-in-page support. Panels with `minSize` override this to keep content visible."},"440":{"id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer-40","page_id":"/docs/components/inline-drawer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/inline-drawer#best-practices","content":"Don't nest InlineDrawers."},"441":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","page_id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","type":"page","content":"MetricsLockup","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Components"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup"},"442":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup-0","page_id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup","content":"The MetricsLockup component displays a single metric with an optional title, info tooltip, trend indicator, and description."},"443":{"id":"/docs/components/metrics-lockup-1","page_id":"/d