ng-and-sizing","content":"**Margins**: 20px top/right, 60px bottom/left for axes and labels"},"1007":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-139","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#responsive-behavior","content":"**Auto-sizing**: Uses VisX's `useParentSize` hook to adapt to container width"},"1008":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-140","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#responsive-behavior","content":"**Horizontal scrolling**: When data points exceed available width, the chart becomes horizontally scrollable"},"1009":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-141","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#responsive-behavior","content":"**Sticky y-axis**: The y-axis remains visible during horizontal scroll"},"1010":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-142","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#responsive-behavior","content":"**Minimum spacing**: Group gaps never fall below 24px, triggering scroll instead"},"1011":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-143","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#accessibility","content":"**Keyboard navigation**: Bar groups are keyboard accessible with `tabIndex={0}` and `role=\"group\"`"},"1012":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-144","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#accessibility","content":"**Screen reader support**: Semantic HTML structure with proper ARIA attributes"},"1013":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-145","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#accessibility","content":"**Tooltips**: Show on both hover and focus for keyboard users"},"1014":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-146","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"The component uses VisX primitives for optimal SVG rendering:"},"1015":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-147","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Scales**: VisX's `scaleBand` and `scaleLinear` for efficient coordinate mapping"},"1016":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-148","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Grouped rendering**: Bars are rendered in SVG `<Group>` elements for logical organization"},"1017":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-149","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#rendering-strategy","content":"**Responsive sizing**: `useParentSize` hook provides efficient resize detection with debouncing (15ms)"},"1018":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-150","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Vertical charts**: Horizontal scrolling when many data points exceed container width"},"1019":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-151","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Horizontal charts**: Vertical scrolling when many categories exceed container height"},"1020":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-152","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#scrolling-strategy","content":"**Sticky axes**: Positioned absolutely to remain visible during scroll"},"1021":{"id":"/docs/components/chart