"✅ Responsive behavior with sticky axes"},"1029":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-161","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"✅ Interactive tooltips"},"1030":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-162","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"✅ Custom domains"},"1031":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-163","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"✅ Design system alignment"},"1032":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-164","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"🚧 RTL compatibility (axis rendering and spacing refinement)"},"1033":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-165","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"🚧 Tick mark positioning improvements"},"1034":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-166","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#development-status","content":"🚧 Additional customization options (tick formatting, axis configuration)"},"1035":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-167","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#bars-not-showing","content":"If bars are not visible:"},"1036":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-168","page_id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart#bars-not-showing","content":"**Check data**: Ensure `series` array has data and `xAccessor`/`yAccessor` return valid values"},"1037":{"id":"/docs/components/chart/bar-chart-169","p